{"tid":579392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普支持槍管：授權警員先拿走危險槍械，遲啲講due process","createTime":"2018-03-03T14:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T04:52:08.000Z","uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"46cfb043f71d588f6fb4bf5d4bc0842e6830e820","tid":579392,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:28:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/3/1/n10183018.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F18%2F3%2F1%2Fn10183018.htm&d=goKayV8uyiD1ycxnCaFcPtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b6488d0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/3/1/n10183018.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2018年03月02日訊】（大紀元記者吳英綜合報導）週三，川普（特朗普）總統在白宮敦促國會議員推動槍枝管制立法，這項倡議與共和黨及步槍協會的主張不同，民主黨則樂觀其成。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，週三（2月28日），川普在電視直播的會議上，要求國會議員重啟槍枝管制立法工作，要求擴大對購槍者的背景審查，包括在槍枝展及互聯網上購槍的人。<br />\n<br />\n川普還提議將購槍年齡限制由18歲提高到21歲、防止精神異常者購槍以及保護校園安全等。此外，川普建議針對攻擊性武器的管制展開對話。<br />\n<br />\n日前在佛州發生的校園重大槍擊案，導致17人遇難，槍枝管制問題再度浮出，引發社會熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n過去，共和黨及全國步槍協會（National Rifle Association，簡稱NRA）向來反對槍枝管制立法。<br />\n<br />\n在會議上，川普建議執法人員應擁有權力，在未獲法院同意的情況下，沒收精神病患或其他危險人士的槍枝。他說：「我傾向支持先沒收，再走該走的法律程序。」<br />\n<br />\n川普說，他最近告訴NRA，「是時候了，我們必須終止這個無意義的事，現在是時候了」。<br />\n<br />\nNRA週三在一份聲明中說，川普的建議是「糟糕的政策」，部分共和黨議員表示，反對槍枝管制立法的立場不變，民主黨方面則是樂觀其成。<br />\n<br />\n川普建議重啟立法工作的核心是2013年兩黨共同提出的一個法案。當年發生桑迪胡克小學（Sandy Hook Elementary School）重大槍擊案後，西弗吉尼亞州民主黨參議員曼欽（Joe Manchin）及賓夕法尼亞州共和黨參議員圖米（Patrick J. Toomey）起草槍枝管制法案，但是遭到多位共和黨議員的反對。<br />\n<br />\n佛羅里達州共和黨參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）週三在會議後仍重申共和黨的立場，那就是，最近的這些槍擊事件並非「那些在槍枝展或停車場購買槍枝的人所為」。"},{"pid":"f9da4f2658eeffed95d6aebfa0630041f5a5a5ae","tid":579392,"uid":76115,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"廢事話english didn't read先貼劣譯<br />\n英文source喺到<br />\n<br />\nTrump to lawmakers: 'Take the gun first, go through due process second' in some cases<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2018/02/28/politics/due-process-donald-trump-second-amendment/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2Fpolitics%2Fdue-process-donald-trump-second-amendment%2Findex.html&d=goKayV8uyiD1ycxnCaFcPtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=be346015\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2Fpolitics%2Fdue-process-donald-trump-second-amendment%2Findex.html&h=207e2e49\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2018/02/28/politics/due-process-donald-trump-second-amendment/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n槍權撚/保守派畀侵侵當狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed4908d2ef4267ab928bf920118638ef94e5ea0","tid":579392,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:31:48.000Z","msg":"特朗普支持槍管：授權警員先拿走危險槍械，遲啲<strong>先</strong>講due process"},{"pid":"62406f9be28464ee5171f9b2d99c6c5e5f323834","tid":579392,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"佢仲同班共和黨講，你地收NRA錢姐，我冇喎"},{"pid":"3d0173548abb77bdc26ab45efbbbd5dddc515881","tid":579392,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde36dec8fa5536378414e20d96a633699840a63","tid":579392,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"共和狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e03a5907e3163ef7b9a0004a7061528df5ce164","tid":579392,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"62406f9be28464ee5171f9b2d99c6c5e5f323834","tid":579392,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03